{"tid":2427001,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"黃洋達:我們熱血團隊 做人最緊要正直","createTime":"2021-02-28T12:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T16:31:28.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8b03759a3504774cbfff994b95f7b9f36142fe96","tid":2427001,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T12:56:56.000Z","msg":"黃洋達:<br />\n近日，針對本人及『熱血公民』的抹黑與誣衊，不斷升級。<br />\n除了不斷散播失實言論，更無聊到在Facebook及其他社交網絡平台，偷取我的相片，開設假帳戶，來假扮我，四處發言生事。<br />\n各位請認清，<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wytat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwytat&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3a3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=ee57d3f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/wytat</a> 才是小弟的臉書帳戶。另外，就是個人專頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pages/%E9%BB%83%E6%B4%8B%E9%81%94/112195718843083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpages%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%25B4%258B%25E9%2581%2594%2F112195718843083&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3a3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=5d1d3bd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/pages/%E9%BB%83%E6%B4%8B%E9%81%94/112195718843083</a><br />\n七一前夕，更有滋事者，假冒『熱血公民』，在facebook開設專頁及發起活動，宣佈虛假的遊行集合地點，擾亂我們的行動。又不斷假冒我的名義開設群組，宣告我們要在九月狙擊某些疑似九東候選人，製造我們團隊旨在分票的效果。更有人冒認『熱血公民』，招募義工。<br />\n請各位認清，『熱血公民』的組群，是這個：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/398005183559992/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F398005183559992%2F&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3a3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=8f7e94f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/398005183559992/</a><br />\n<br />\n敬請各位朋友注意。<br />\n<br />\n這些做法，當然可恥。然而這也反映了，我們對很多心中只有議席的政團做成巨大威脅。<br />\n我們熱血團隊，秉持熱血政治精神：「做人最緊要正直」，各位手足，我們不怕打壓抹黑，這些攻擊，是對我們工作的認同。我們不會向對手作抹黑攻擊，不搞黑材料。<br />\n奉勸其他政團，要保持信心，做好工作，不要因為信心不足，而誤入岐途。may the force be with you，小心不要墮入Dark side，慎之。"},{"pid":"9876833c014ca986112cb0b7cff70f6252e225ee","tid":2427001,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T12:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071e4ef8269ad6d84d8dbf6c6c93e4394ef4e3e9","tid":2427001,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T12:58:09.000Z","msg":"忠誠就可以"},{"pid":"e1182fcb73c842eb6c8fc3138215ad1cb862bb7d","tid":2427001,"uid":54496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"同香港黑警講既野咁似既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad8ad42d476c41579ed1a9140d19de6178381d8","tid":2427001,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1182fcb73c842eb6c8fc3138215ad1cb862bb7d","tid":2427001,"uid":54496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"同香港黑警講既野咁似既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"熱血公民上上下下都好正直"},{"pid":"cd1602cf4978610f81b8ff92cfc60781ab551044","tid":2427001,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"何淦途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cc40a5b047eca8815642035fd1266cd2e6c029","tid":2427001,"uid":19113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"全港唯一合法抗爭團伙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130b08d1e25f1f61f4a59d7aa6d074e88d337265","tid":2427001,"uid":291465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"熱狗正直? Fxxk off<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22001216ea78f92bca917989e2b7ad9dcb1dd0e8","tid":2427001,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:31:28.000Z","msg":"第三個字就係講針"}]}